DESCRIPTION
-------------
This simple configuration simulates the surface well-mixed 10 m of a
water column in the Southern Ocean.
The parameters of the analytical forcings are tweaked to reproduce the southern
hemisphere seasonality.
All organic matter is remineralized in the layer.

REQUIREMENTS
--------------
The code must be compiled with the following keys
INCLUDE_PELFE
INCLUDE_PELCO2

The following configuration must be specified in config_STANDALONE.sh
GlobalDefsBFM.model.iron
